To plot indicator values, in the OnData event handler, call the Plot method.

private ThreeLineStrike _threelinestrike;

// In Initialize()
var symbol = AddEquity("SPY").Symbol;
_threelinestrike = ThreeLineStrike(symbol);

// In OnData()
if (_threelinestrike.IsReady)
{
    Plot("My Indicators", "threelinestrike", _threelinestrike.Current);
